294
00:15:59,750 --> 00:16:00,790
No way.

295
00:16:25,320 --> 00:16:27,030
What you said that day,

296
00:16:28,670 --> 00:16:30,200
were you serious?

297
00:16:31,720 --> 00:16:32,320
Which day?

298
00:16:35,910 --> 00:16:37,600
I need you to be my boyfriend.

299
00:16:38,670 --> 00:16:40,390
Me to your boyfriend.

300
00:16:41,480 --> 00:16:43,000
Was that serious?

301
00:16:50,120 --> 00:16:51,120
What do you think?

302
00:16:58,360 --> 00:16:59,870
I'll stay!

303
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:02,720
Where are you going?

304
00:17:08,200 --> 00:17:09,400
Go back by yourself!

305
00:17:22,270 --> 00:17:22,790
Guang.

306
00:17:23,200 --> 00:17:23,750
Kun.

307
00:17:28,030 --> 00:17:28,970
Don't move.

308
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:29,530
Lie down.

309
00:17:31,240 --> 00:17:32,830
I made you some millet porridge

310
00:17:32,830 --> 00:17:33,880
with veggies

311
00:17:34,240 --> 00:17:36,370
and stewed the meat until it's tender.

312
00:17:36,590 --> 00:17:37,400
Drink up.

313
00:17:38,270 --> 00:17:38,790
Kun,

314
00:17:40,240 --> 00:17:42,350
I want to take this off.

315
00:17:42,550 --> 00:17:43,350
You can't.

316
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:45,510
When can I take it off?

317
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:46,960
Whenever

318
00:17:47,240 --> 00:17:48,170
the doctor says.

319
00:17:51,270 --> 00:17:52,600
It's so uncomfortable.

320
00:17:53,030 --> 00:17:53,630
Oh, right.

321
00:17:53,920 --> 00:17:54,780
Let me show you.

322
00:18:06,000 --> 00:18:06,330
Here.

323
00:18:06,920 --> 00:18:07,250
Look.

324
00:18:08,510 --> 00:18:09,840
The baby's doing great.

325
00:18:09,980 --> 00:18:11,330
Seems like he's gotten chubbier.

326
00:18:11,330 --> 00:18:12,850
He sure has put on some weight.

327
00:18:12,850 --> 00:18:14,510
My arms get tired holding him.

328
00:18:15,940 --> 00:18:17,270
Why is the screen black?

329
00:18:18,800 --> 00:18:20,600
You just stay here and rest easy.

330
00:18:20,880 --> 00:18:22,740
Shulan will take care of the baby.

331
00:18:23,070 --> 00:18:24,530
If you want to find Wen Wen,

332
00:18:24,830 --> 00:18:26,830
have the guys help you out.

333
00:18:27,880 --> 00:18:29,110
Don't worry about anything.

334
00:18:29,110 --> 00:18:31,110
I feel relieved with you and Shulan

335
00:18:32,270 --> 00:18:33,600
taking care of the baby.

336
00:18:36,310 --> 00:18:36,750
Kun,

337
00:18:39,270 --> 00:18:40,400
I've been thinking

338
00:18:40,830 --> 00:18:43,030
that you should give the baby a name.

339
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:45,110
Have you thought of one?

340
00:18:45,110 --> 00:18:46,720
I shouldn't name him.

341
00:18:47,030 --> 00:18:49,030
You're the father, so it's up to you.

342
00:18:49,270 --> 00:18:49,960
Once you've decided,

343
00:18:49,960 --> 00:18:50,960
I can tell Shulan.

344
00:18:51,310 --> 00:18:54,040
She's been calling the baby
"good boy" every day.

345
00:18:58,750 --> 00:19:00,350
My name doesn't sound good.

346
00:19:01,240 --> 00:19:02,270
Li Yuanguang—

347
00:19:03,770 --> 00:19:06,100
