348
00:19:07,110 --> 00:19:08,680
I hope my kid

349
00:19:10,110 --> 00:19:12,350
will grow up brightly.

350
00:19:13,030 --> 00:19:14,560
Then call him "Liangtang."

351
00:19:16,440 --> 00:19:17,900
Doesn't sound like a name.

352
00:19:21,550 --> 00:19:22,810
How about Liangliang?

353
00:19:23,960 --> 00:19:24,690
Liangliang.

354
00:19:25,880 --> 00:19:27,740
Living a bright and upright life.

355
00:19:29,030 --> 00:19:29,690
That works.

356
00:19:30,480 --> 00:19:31,210
Sounds good.

357
00:19:34,400 --> 00:19:35,860
If anything happens to me,

358
00:19:36,640 --> 00:19:37,400
Liangliang

359
00:19:38,350 --> 00:19:40,150
