366
00:19:57,270 --> 00:19:58,070
You're wrong.

367
00:19:58,960 --> 00:20:00,220
This wasn't about you.

368
00:20:00,880 --> 00:20:01,740
It was about me.

369
00:20:03,340 --> 00:20:05,770
You took the beating for me.

370
00:20:06,920 --> 00:20:07,510
Why?

371
00:20:08,350 --> 00:20:11,160
