372
00:20:14,880 --> 00:20:15,750
Zhao Youlin.

373
00:20:20,750 --> 00:20:21,550
Just wait.

374
00:20:22,200 --> 00:20:23,160
This isn't over.

375
00:20:24,310 --> 00:20:25,970
That guy is really heartless.

376
00:20:26,750 --> 00:20:28,750
I heard the Hedong guy was arrested.

377
00:20:29,240 --> 00:20:31,110
Don't get into trouble because of me.

378
00:20:31,110 --> 00:20:32,310
What is Zhao Youlin?

379
00:20:33,350 --> 00:20:35,070
A wall standing in our way.

380
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:38,600
Now we only have two choices.

381
00:20:40,110 --> 00:20:42,170
Either we turn back and admit defeat,

382
00:20:43,000 --> 00:20:45,200
letting him step on us forever,

383
00:20:45,830 --> 00:20:48,030
or we charge forward and knock him down.

384
00:20:48,240 --> 00:20:49,900
What do you think we should do?

385
00:21:06,060 --> 00:21:06,750
Captain Qi,

386
00:21:07,190 --> 00:21:08,790
are you setting up an ambush?

387
00:21:11,510 --> 00:21:12,920
Still haven't found the Liang gang's

388
00:21:12,920 --> 00:21:13,720
gravedigger.

389
00:21:13,960 --> 00:21:15,020
It's frustrating.

390
00:21:16,720 --> 00:21:17,380
Captain Qi,

391
00:21:17,640 --> 00:21:18,750
don't you think

392
00:21:20,110 --> 00:21:21,240
that what Liang told us

393
00:21:21,240 --> 00:21:24,440
about the person who sold him
explosives is a bit suspicious?

394
00:21:24,440 --> 00:21:25,840
I'm thinking of someone.

395
00:21:27,400 --> 00:21:28,060
The Gunner.

396
00:21:28,160 --> 00:21:28,560
Right.

397
00:21:30,030 --> 00:21:32,290
It's a pity this Gunner is so mysterious.

398
00:21:32,750 --> 00:21:34,950
He hasn't surfaced for all these years.

399
00:21:35,590 --> 00:21:36,550
This time he has.

400
00:21:37,440 --> 00:21:39,720
We analyzed the explosives used

401
00:21:40,160 --> 00:21:41,030
in the Yin Village tomb,

402
00:21:41,030 --> 00:21:41,890
and found that

403
00:21:41,920 --> 00:21:43,000
the mix is nearly identical to

404
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:44,460
the one used by Uncle Gang

405
00:21:44,480 --> 00:21:45,410
in recent years.

406
00:21:46,590 --> 00:21:49,510
You mean the thieves
are from Uncle Gang,

407
00:21:49,680 --> 00:21:50,960
and the Gunner...

408
00:21:52,550 --> 00:21:53,400
is too?

409
00:21:54,790 --> 00:21:55,640
Perhaps.

410
00:21:57,680 --> 00:21:59,550
Do you think this Uncle

411
00:22:00,880 --> 00:22:02,160
is Mu Jianhui?

412
00:22:02,830 --> 00:22:03,960
I wouldn't say that.

413
00:22:04,960 --> 00:22:05,400
Right.

414
00:22:06,480 --> 00:22:08,720
We don't have any evidence now.

415
00:22:09,960 --> 00:22:12,240
It's hard to expose Uncle Gang.

416
00:22:13,160 --> 00:22:13,880
Unless...

417
00:22:14,030 --> 00:22:15,400
Unless King Hua gets caught.

418
00:22:15,400 --> 00:22:15,800
Right.

419
00:22:16,750 --> 00:22:18,350
Just wait for the right time.

420
00:22:18,680 --> 00:22:20,350
When King Hua gets exposed,

421
00:22:20,480 --> 00:22:22,750
and Liang's arrested,

422
00:22:23,440 --> 00:22:24,640
where can Uncle hide?

423
00:22:31,030 --> 00:22:32,430
Well, we know so little

424
00:22:33,790 --> 00:22:35,160
about King Hua.

425
00:22:36,240 --> 00:22:38,920
It's been nearly 10 years
since the black pottery figurine case.

426
00:22:38,920 --> 00:22:40,850
Like we've been fighting a shadow.

427
00:22:41,140 --> 00:22:41,740
Oh, right.

428
00:22:42,110 --> 00:22:43,960
I've redrawn the portrait based on Liang's

429
00:22:43,960 --> 00:22:45,310
description of King Hua,

430
00:22:45,310 --> 00:22:46,640
and double-checked their

431
00:22:46,640 --> 00:22:47,880
communication records.

