00:22:51,310 --> 00:22:52,200
It seems that

435
00:22:52,640 --> 00:22:54,200
King Hua is most

436
00:22:54,270 --> 00:22:56,000
likely around Xingfu Village.

437
00:22:59,960 --> 00:23:01,000
Xingfu Village.

438
00:23:24,440 --> 00:23:26,350
A place where all sorts mingle.

439
00:23:26,720 --> 00:23:28,200
A perfect hiding spot.

440
00:23:29,200 --> 00:23:30,440
Remember back then,

441
00:23:31,240 --> 00:23:33,720
when we were chasing King Hua
in the black pottery figurine case?

442
00:23:33,720 --> 00:23:34,550
Yes.

443
00:23:35,070 --> 00:23:36,730
He loved hiding in small inns.

444
00:23:36,920 --> 00:23:38,120
Pity that he got away.

445
00:23:39,400 --> 00:23:41,530
If he's hiding here, how do we find him?

446
00:23:41,880 --> 00:23:42,940
Use the old method.

447
00:23:45,000 --> 00:23:45,860
The old method?

448
00:23:48,480 --> 00:23:49,200
Wide net?

449
00:23:50,880 --> 00:23:52,440
Blanket search?

450
00:23:52,880 --> 00:23:54,010
No one gets left out.

451
00:23:55,030 --> 00:23:57,240
But you know how many
buildings are in this village

452
00:23:57,240 --> 00:23:58,000
and how many people live here?

453
00:23:58,000 --> 00:23:58,830
How do we investigate?

454
00:23:58,830 --> 00:23:59,960
Just wander around?

455
00:24:01,920 --> 00:24:03,270
Sometimes

456
00:24:03,790 --> 00:24:06,590
