457
00:24:07,510 --> 00:24:08,710
Got any better ideas?

458
00:24:09,750 --> 00:24:10,680
Any strategies?

459
00:24:12,960 --> 00:24:14,090
You're impressive.

460
00:24:34,830 --> 00:24:36,230
I found the book you want.

461
00:24:40,510 --> 00:24:41,720
