00:25:08,030 --> 00:25:09,160
I want this book?

467
00:25:10,830 --> 00:25:12,030
If you want to tell me,

468
00:25:12,790 --> 00:25:14,320
you'd have said it already.

469
00:25:14,920 --> 00:25:16,050
Do I even need to ask?

470
00:25:21,550 --> 00:25:24,200
How come I never noticed before

471
00:25:26,240 --> 00:25:28,200
