472
00:25:31,510 --> 00:25:32,310
Before,

473
00:25:33,070 --> 00:25:34,530
you were like a wild goose—

474
00:25:35,200 --> 00:25:36,660
Whenever I say something,

475
00:25:36,750 --> 00:25:37,880
you'd snap at me.

476
00:25:39,920 --> 00:25:41,790
You should thank me.

477
00:25:42,160 --> 00:25:43,070
If I hadn't always

478
00:25:43,070 --> 00:25:44,350
gone against you,

479
00:25:45,090 --> 00:25:46,950
you'd have caused more troubles.

480
00:26:14,160 --> 00:26:15,820
You kept it especially for me?

481
00:26:18,750 --> 00:26:19,640
Of course.

482
00:26:24,790 --> 00:26:25,990
