00:27:36,750 --> 00:27:38,160
nowadays, high-tech methods

492
00:27:38,160 --> 00:27:39,200
are increasingly used in

493
00:27:39,200 --> 00:27:41,000
archaeological applications.

494
00:27:41,110 --> 00:27:42,440
We hope you can use

495
00:27:42,440 --> 00:27:43,790
geophysical and geochemical

496
00:27:43,790 --> 00:27:45,480
exploration technologies

497
00:27:45,920 --> 00:27:48,050
to help us analyze the soil structure.

498
00:27:48,110 --> 00:27:50,110
This will also serve as a verification

499
00:27:50,110 --> 00:27:52,070
of our previous
archaeological exploration work.

500
00:27:52,070 --> 00:27:52,600
Alright.

501
00:27:52,750 --> 00:27:53,750
Thank you for your hard work.

502
00:27:53,750 --> 00:27:54,750
Don't mention it.

503
00:28:05,510 --> 00:28:07,440
