507
00:28:13,790 --> 00:28:15,250
That's quite impressive.

508
00:28:17,640 --> 00:28:18,770
Heizui, look at him.

509
00:28:22,240 --> 00:28:23,370
Where are you going?

510
00:28:23,680 --> 00:28:25,160
I've received an order.

511
00:28:25,680 --> 00:28:28,160
Your girl Qing went all the way
to the site to find me,

512
00:28:28,160 --> 00:28:29,500
asking me to bring you along

513
00:28:29,500 --> 00:28:31,430
to look for some stone slab.

514
00:28:31,880 --> 00:28:33,680
Are you looking for stone slabs?

515
00:28:36,550 --> 00:28:37,880
You're so lucky.

516
00:28:39,160 --> 00:28:41,200
That young lady is pretty, careful,

517
00:28:41,440 --> 00:28:42,970
sincere and genuine to you.

518
00:28:43,000 --> 00:28:44,590
I approve of your marriage.

519
00:28:49,510 --> 00:28:50,040
Let's go.

520
00:28:51,350 --> 00:28:52,080
Captain Luo.

521
00:28:52,200 --> 00:28:52,680
Today,

522
00:28:52,680 --> 00:28:54,810
