523
00:28:55,000 --> 00:28:57,030
We've seen
ground-penetrating radar before,

524
00:28:57,030 --> 00:28:59,000
as we've used it
quite often in archaeology.

525
00:28:59,000 --> 00:29:00,960
Yes, it's also known as

526
00:29:01,030 --> 00:29:03,160
the "Eye of Geophysical Prospecting."

527
00:29:03,160 --> 00:29:05,360
It can detect underground structures,

528
00:29:05,440 --> 00:29:07,510
such as rocks and soil,

529
00:29:07,790 --> 00:29:11,320
as well as man-made materials
like gravel and concrete bricks.

530
00:29:11,750 --> 00:29:12,830
Besides the ground-penetrating radar,

531
00:29:12,830 --> 00:29:14,240
we've also brought

532
00:29:14,270 --> 00:29:16,640
high-density electrical resistivity meters
and radon detectors this time.

533
00:29:16,640 --> 00:29:17,840
What? What detector?

534
00:29:18,160 --> 00:29:19,090
Radon detector.

535
00:29:19,790 --> 00:29:20,520
It mainly can

536
00:29:20,530 --> 00:29:23,010
detect whether there's radon in the gas

537
00:29:23,510 --> 00:29:25,770
