538
00:29:26,330 --> 00:29:27,410
This radon

539
00:29:27,440 --> 00:29:29,000
is a common element

540
00:29:29,070 --> 00:29:30,960
in our natural world.

541
00:29:31,480 --> 00:29:34,200
For example, granite,
