00:30:05,830 --> 00:30:06,790
How do I use this?

557
00:30:07,830 --> 00:30:08,430
Move back.

558
00:30:10,880 --> 00:30:11,410
Let's go.

559
00:30:14,590 --> 00:30:15,990
Captain Yang, what's up?

560
00:30:16,160 --> 00:30:16,890
